        "zh": "是关于信息安全管理体系的标准。ISO 27001规定了后文所述的「信息安全管理体系（ISMS）」（p.503）。",
        "en": "A standard for information security management systems. ISO 27001 specifies the \"ISMS (Information Security Management System)\" (p.503) described later."
